on any other vehicle
i have on stock.

01:02:41.492 --> 01:02:43.191
No, I think I'm done
with the runaround.

01:02:43.193 --> 01:02:44.793
But I'll be sure
to let the better
business bureau

01:02:44.795 --> 01:02:47.028
know about
your practices.

01:02:47.030 --> 01:02:49.364
Then maybe next time
you'll think twice
about telling a customer

01:02:49.366 --> 01:02:51.366
you have a car
in inventory
when you don't.

01:02:51.368 --> 01:02:54.069
Again, sheri,
that wasn't the case at all.

01:02:54.071 --> 01:02:55.504
Oh, well,
i think it was.

01:02:55.506 --> 01:02:57.906
And you'll be hearing
from my senator as well.

01:02:59.209 --> 01:03:00.342
Your senator?

01:03:00.344 --> 01:03:01.476
Heh. Wow.

01:03:01.478 --> 01:03:03.545
You know, usually
customers threaten

01:03:03.547 --> 01:03:06.414
to sic the attorney
general on me,
but a senator,

01:03:06.416 --> 01:03:09.851
well played, sheri,
really well played.

01:03:09.853 --> 01:03:12.988
And what, I suppose
you've got him
on direct dial?

01:03:12.990 --> 01:03:14.556
You know, I put
millions of dollars...

01:03:14.558 --> 01:03:16.258
Where are we at?
Look right here.

01:03:16.260 --> 01:03:18.960
...and I can't get him
to return my calls,

01:03:18.962 --> 01:03:20.529
so good luck
with that, sweetheart.

01:03:22.031 --> 01:03:23.365
Hey, Reynolds, how's
the selling coming?

01:03:23.367 --> 01:03:27.169
I hope that little bitch
does call her senator.

01:03:27.171 --> 01:03:29.271
Fix it. Go.

01:03:29.273 --> 01:03:31.540
Yo, boss, I got one.

01:03:31.542 --> 01:03:32.908
There's a couple
