01:03:34.211 --> 01:03:35.477
and they're looking
for a new one.

01:03:35.479 --> 01:03:37.012
Okay, relax.
Did they pick out
a car yet?

01:03:37.014 --> 01:03:38.079
No, not yet. I think
they're looking--

01:03:38.081 --> 01:03:39.114
Christian, please,

01:03:39.116 --> 01:03:40.215
can you take
the puppy outside?

01:03:40.217 --> 01:03:41.850
Come on.

01:03:41.852 --> 01:03:44.119
Let's get you
outside before you
piss yourself.

01:03:44.121 --> 01:03:45.187
Fuck, yeah.

01:03:45.189 --> 01:03:47.322
All right, everybody,
listen up!

01:03:47.324 --> 01:03:50.358
It's 2:15, and we are
sitting on 20 cars,

01:03:50.360 --> 01:03:54.262
which means we have
less than three hours
and 15 cars to go!

01:03:54.264 --> 01:03:57.499
That means there are
15 people in the great
state of Arizona

01:03:57.501 --> 01:04:00.368
