for you to connect them
with a new vehicle.

01:04:00.370 --> 01:04:02.437
What do you say
we make that happen?

01:04:02.439 --> 01:04:04.406
Time to rock-'n'-roll!
Let's go! Let's go!

01:04:09.546 --> 01:04:10.979
Hi.

01:04:13.517 --> 01:04:15.016
What do you think, man?

01:04:24.628 --> 01:04:26.027
He said he wants
to pay invoice.

01:04:26.029 --> 01:04:27.929
Tell him when he
rounds up $10 million,

01:04:27.931 --> 01:04:30.966
he can buy his own store
and pay invoice for
any car he likes,

01:04:30.968 --> 01:04:32.300
but until then,
that's the price.

01:04:32.302 --> 01:04:34.236
I'm making no money
off of this deal,

01:04:34.238 --> 01:04:35.871
just so you know.

01:04:35.873 --> 01:04:38.173
And I still have to pay
these two guys commission.

01:04:38.175 --> 01:04:40.642
You see 'em? All right?
So do we got a deal?

01:04:40.644 --> 01:04:43.245
Safety and
fuel economy, okay?

01:04:43.247 --> 01:04:44.479
25 mpg city...

01:04:44.481 --> 01:04:46.481
I think
we have a match.

01:04:46.483 --> 01:04:50.051
I love your hair
with the color
of this car.

01:04:50.053 --> 01:04:52.354
How 'bout now?

01:05:00.530 --> 01:05:01.529
Watch and learn.

