Just sold one to Katy Perry.

01:05:03.567 --> 01:05:05.000
Woman: Oh!
Same color.

01:05:05.002 --> 01:05:06.568
Oh, my god.
It has Bluetooth...

01:05:06.570 --> 01:05:09.137
Fisher, hi.
Heard the divorce is final.

01:05:09.139 --> 01:05:12.007
I have a lot of convertibles
i think you'd be
interested in.

01:05:32.062 --> 01:05:33.495
What's that
gonna cost us?

01:05:33.497 --> 01:05:35.363
No, it comes
with the car, sweetie.

01:05:35.365 --> 01:05:37.132
Yeah, sweetie,
it comes with the car.

01:05:42.539 --> 01:05:45.206
I was only
able to--bam!

01:05:46.376 --> 01:05:48.944
Hey, let's go ring
the big bell.

