01:06:30.520 --> 01:06:33.521
Singer: What? Extra?
It'll be all good. Don't...

01:06:37.294 --> 01:06:38.626
I love this car
for you.

01:06:38.628 --> 01:06:40.395
So what do we think?
I love it.

01:06:40.397 --> 01:06:42.163
I'll tell you
after I see the numbers.

01:06:43.166 --> 01:06:44.632
Nice rally.

01:06:44.634 --> 01:06:47.202
I can't wait
for that pep talk
come Monday.

01:06:47.204 --> 01:06:48.203
Save it.

01:06:51.107 --> 01:06:53.108
We got a live one, <i>jefe.</i>

01:06:54.577 --> 01:06:56.444
I got 'em downing
l-tryptophan dogs
as we speak,

01:06:56.446 --> 01:06:58.179
so I figure
in about 15 minutes,

01:06:58.181 --> 01:07:00.081
I'll have 'em right
where I want 'em, comatose.

01:07:00.083 --> 01:07:01.649
That's good,
because right now,

01:07:01.651 --> 01:07:03.351
we are sitting
at 299,

